WHO   — Scytale — the Tleilaxu Face Dancer
WHAT  — A Tleilaxu Face Dancer — a shapeshifter who can take the form and voice of others.
WHERE — D1 · Dune  Framework inputs: Dune Messiah and the wider saga — the works of the Bene Tleilax  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — He is the inscrutable hand of forbidden biology, trafficking in cloned flesh and stolen identity against the rising power of Paul.
HOW   — He wears stolen faces, and as a conspirator offers a ghola of the dead Duncan Idaho as a poisoned gift.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  A face that is never his own, offered like a gift with poison underneath.

